snippet.title: All You Can Eat JAPANESE STEAK BUFFET With Amber Liu
snippet.description:
A special guest who's a Kpop star, Amber Liu from f(x) joined me to eat at an all you can eat #japanese steak #buffet in LA. While we eat our way through some amazing a5 #wagyu beef I asked Amber all about the Kpop world so I hope you enjoy and get to know about how to become a Kpop star! :-)

Location:
✧ Shinobu Japanese BBQ
15202 Goldenwest St, Westminster, CA 92683

IG: ajol_llama

Check out Amber's Tour X tickets:
http://www.amberliuofficial.com/tickets/
